\c 24
\s UIsaka uganwa nguRebeka
\p
\v 1 UAbrahama wayesemdala eselensuku ezinengi\f + \fk elensuku ezinengi: \fl Heb. \fq eqhubekile ngezinsuku.\f*; leN\nd kosi\nd* yayimbusisile kukho konke\x + 13.2; 14.14; 24.35.\x*.
\v 2 UAbrahama wasesithi encekwini yakhe, endala yendlu yakhe\x + 15.2.\x*, ebusa phezu kwakho konke alakho\x + 24.10.\x*: Ake ubeke isandla sakho ngaphansi kwethangazi lami\x + 47.29.\x*,
\v 3 ukuze ngikufungise\x + 14.22.\x* ngeN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamazulu loNkulunkulu womhlaba, ukuthi kawuyikuyithathela indodana yami umfazi emadodakazini amaKhanani\x + 26.34,35; 27.46.\x*, engihlala phakathi kwawo;
\v 4 kodwa uzakuya\x + 28.2.\x* elizweni lakithi lezihlotsheni zami\x + 11.31; 22.20-24; 27.43.\x*, uyithathele umfazi indodana yami uIsaka.
\v 5 Inceku yasisithi kuye: Mhlawumbe owesifazana angafuni ukungilandela kulelilizwe, ngingayibuyisela lokuyibuyisela yini indodana yakho elizweni owaphuma kulo?
\v 6 UAbrahama wasesithi kuye: Qaphela ukuthi ungayibuyiseli khona indodana yami.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wamazulu, eyangithatha endlini kababa\x + 12.1.\x* lelizweni lokuzalwa kwami, eyakhuluma kimi, eyafunga kimi isithi: Ngizalinika inzalo yakho lelilizwe\x + 12.7; 13.15; 15.18; 17.8; 26.4. Seb. 7.5.\x*; yona izathuma ingilosi yayo phambi kwakho\x + Eks. 23.20,23; 33.2. Heb. 1.14.\x*, ukuze uyithathele khona umfazi indodana yami.
\v 8 Kodwa uba owesifazana engafuni ukukulandela, uzakuba ukhululekile kulesisifungo sami\x + Josh. 2.20.\x*; kuphela ungayibuyiseli indodana yami khona.
\v 9 Inceku yasibeka isandla sayo ngaphansi kwethangazi likaAbrahama\x + 24.2.\x* inkosi yayo, yafunga kuye ngaloludaba.
\p
\v 10 Njalo inceku yasithatha amakamela\x + 12.16.\x* alitshumi kuwo amakamela enkosi yayo, yahamba, lakho konke okuhle kwenkosi yayo kwakusesandleni sayo, yasisukuma yaya eMesopotamiya emzini kaNahori\x + 24.24; 27.43.\x*.
\v 11 Yasiguqisa amakamela ngaphandle komuzi emthonjeni wamanzi ngesikhathi santambama, ngesikhathi sokuphuma kwabakhi\x + Eks. 2.16. 1 Sam. 9.11. 29.9.\x* bamanzi besifazana.
\v 12 Yasisithi: N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wenkosi yami uAbrahama\x + 24.27,42; 17.7; 26.24; 28.13; 32.9. Eks. 3.6,15.\x*, ake ungiphumelelise lamuhla, uyenzele umusa inkosi yami uAbrahama\x + 27.20. Hlab. 37.5.\x*.
\v 13 Khangela, ngimi emthonjeni wamanzi\x + 24.43.\x*, kuphuma amadodakazi amadoda omuzi ukukha amanzi\x + 29.9,10.\x*.
\v 14 Njalo kuzakuthi intombazana engizakuthi kuyo: Ake ukhothamise imbiza yakho ukuze nginathe, ibisisithi: Natha, lamakamela akho ngizawanathisa; yiyo oyimisele inceku yakho uIsaka; ngalokho-ke ngizakwazi\x + 15.8.\x* ukuthi uyenzele umusa inkosi yami.
\v 15 Kwasekusithi ingakaqedi ukukhuluma, khangela-ke, uRebeka waphuma, owazalelwa uBethuweli indodana kaMilka\x + 11.29; 22.23.\x*, umkaNahori umfowabo kaAbrahama, njalo elembiza ehlombe lakhe.
\v 16 Njalo inkazana yayikhangeleka kuhle kakhulu\x + 26.7.\x*, intombi emsulwa, okungelandoda eyaziyo; yasisehlela emthonjeni, yagcwalisa imbiza yayo, yenyuka.
\v 17 Inceku yasigijima ukuyihlangabeza yathi: Ake unginathise amanzi amalutshwana embizeni yakho.
\v 18 Yasisithi: Natha, nkosi yami. Yaphangisa yehlisela imbiza yayo esandleni sayo, yayinathisa.
\v 19 Isiqedile ukuyinathisa yathi: Ngizakhelela lamakamela akho aze aqede ukunatha.
\v 20 Yasiphangisa yathululela isigxingi sayo emkolweni wokunathela, yabuya yagijimela emthonjeni ukuyakukha, yakhelelela amakamela ayo wonke.
\v 21 Indoda yasiyikhangelisisa ithule ukuze yazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* iyiphumelelisile indlela yayo kumbe hatshi\x + 24.12,40,42,56. Neh. 1.11.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Kwasekusithi amakamela eseqedile ukunatha, indoda yasithatha icici legolide, osisindo salo sasiyingxenye \w yeshekeli\w**, lamasongo amabili ezandleni zayo, isisindo sawo saba ngama\add shekeli\add* alitshumi egolide.
\v 23 Yasisithi: Uyindodakazi kabani? Ake utsho. Kukhona indawo yethu yini endlini kayihlo ukuthi silale?
\v 24 Yasisithi kuyo: Ngiyindodakazi kaBethuweli indodana kaMilka owayizalela uNahori\x + 24.15.\x*.
\v 25 Yathi kuyo futhi: Silakho konke amahlanga lokudla kwezinyamazana okunengi, lendawo yokulala.
\v 26 Indoda yasikhothama\x + 24.48,52. Eks. 4.31.\x*, yakhonza iN\nd kosi\nd*,
\v 27 yasisithi: Ibusisiwe iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu wenkosi yami uAbrahama, engayekelanga umusa wayo lobuqotho bayo\x + 32.10. Hlab. 98.3.\x* enkosini yami; mina-ke, ngisendleleni, iN\nd kosi\nd* ingikhokhelele endlini yabafowabo benkosi yami\x + 24.48.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Intombi yasigijima, yazisa \add abe\add*ndlu kanina ngalezizinto.
\v 29 Njalo uRebeka wayelomnewabo obizo lakhe lalinguLabani\x + 25.20; 28.2; 29.5.\x*; uLabani wasegijimela phandle endodeni emthonjeni.
\v 30 Kwasekusithi esebonile icici lamasongo ezandleni zikadadewabo, esezwile amazwi kaRebeka udadewabo okuthi: Itsho njalo indoda kimi; wasesiya endodeni, khangela-ke, yayimi ngasemakameleni emthonjeni.
\v 31 Wasesithi: Ngena wena obusisiweyo weN\nd kosi\x + 26.29. Hlu. 17.2. Ruthe 3.10.\x*\nd*; umeleni ngaphandle? Ngoba mina sengilungisile indlu lendawo yamakamela.
\p
\v 32 Indoda yasisiza endlini, yakhulula amakamela; wasenika amakamela amahlanga lokudla kwenyamazana\x + 43.24. Hlu. 19.21.\x*, lamanzi okugeza inyawo zayo lenyawo zamadoda ayelayo\x + 18.4; 19.2; 43.24.\x*.
\v 33 Kwasekubekwa ukudla phambi kwayo; kodwa yathi: Kangiyikudla ngize ngikhulume indaba zami. Wasesithi: Khuluma.
\v 34 Yasisithi: Ngiyinceku kaAbrahama.
\v 35 Futhi iN\nd kosi\nd* iyibusisile kakhulu inkosi yami\x + 24.1.\x*, yaze yaba nkulu. Yayinika izimvu lezinkomo, lesiliva legolide, lezinceku lezincekukazi, lamakamela labobabhemi.
\v 36 Njalo uSara inkosikazi yenkosi yami uyizalele inkosi yami indodana emva kokuba esemdala\x + 21.2.\x*; yasiyinika konke elakho\x + 25.5.\x*.
\v 37 Inkosi yami yasingifungisa\x + 24.3.\x* isithi: Ungayithatheli indodana yami umfazi kumadodakazi amaKhanani, engihlala elizweni lawo;
\v 38 kodwa uzakuya endlini kababa lezihlotsheni zami\x + 24.4.\x*, ubusuyithathela indodana yami umfazi.
\v 39 Ngasengisithi enkosini yami: Mhlawumbe owesifazana kayikungilandela\x + 24.5.\x*.
\v 40 Yasisithi kimi: IN\nd kosi\x + 24.7.\x*\nd*, engihamba phambi kwayo\x + 17.1.\x*, izathuma ingilosi yayo lawe, izaphumelelisa indlela yakho\x + 24.21.\x*, njalo uzayithathela indodana yami umfazi ezihlotsheni zami lendlini kababa.
\v 41 Emva kwalokho uzakhululeka esifungweni sami\x + 24.8.\x* uba uye ezihlotsheni zami njalo uba bengakuniki yena, uzakhululeka-ke esifungweni sami.
\v 42 Kuthe ngifika emthonjeni lamuhla, ngathi: N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wenkosi yami uAbrahama\x + 24.12.\x*, uba-ke uphumelelisa indlela yami, engihamba ngayo\x + 24.21.\x*;
\v 43 khangela, ngimi emthonjeni wamanzi\x + 24.13.\x*; njalo kakuthi intombi ezaphuma ukukha lengizakuthi kuyo: Ake unginathise amanzi amalutshwana esigxingini sakho;
\v 44 ibisisithi kimi: Natha lawe, futhi ngizakhelelela lamakamela akho\x + 24.14,15.\x*; \add kayibe\add* nguye owesifazana iN\nd kosi\nd* emmisele indodana yenkosi yami\x + 20.16; 21.25.\x*.
\v 45 Ngingakaqedi ukukhuluma enhliziyweni yami\x + 1 Sam. 1.13.\x*, khangela-ke, uRebeka waphuma lesigxingi sisehlombe lakhe; wehlela emthonjeni, wakha. Ngasengisithi kuye: Akunginathise.
\v 46 Wasephangisa, wethula isigxingi kuye\x + 24.22. Hez. 16.11,12.\x* wathi: Natha, futhi ngizanathisa lamakamela akho. Ngasenginatha, wasenathisa lamakamela.
\v 47 Ngasengimbuza ngathi: Uyindodakazi kabani? Wasesithi: Indodakazi kaBethuweli, indodana kaNahori uMilka amzalela yona; ngasengifaka icici emakhaleni akhe lamasongo ezandleni zakhe.
\v 48 Ngasengikhothama\x + 24.26,52.\x*, ngakhonza iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngabusisa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenkosi yami uAbrahama, engikhokhele endleleni elungileyo ukuthi indodakazi yomfowabo wenkosi yami ngiyithathele indodana yayo\x + 22.23. 2 Kho. 8.26.\x*.
\v 49 Khathesi-ke uba lizayenzela inkosi yami umusa lobuqotho\x + 47.29. Josh. 2.14.\x*, ngitshelani; uba-ke kungenjalo, ngitshelani, ukuze ngiphendukele ngakwesokunene loba ngakwesokhohlo.
\p
\v 50 Khona oLabani loBethuweli baphendula, bathi: Le into ivela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; kasilakutsho lutho kuwe, olubi kumbe oluhle\x + 31.24. 2 Sam. 13.22.\x*.
\v 51 Khangela, uRebeka uphambi kwakho; \add m\add*thathe uhambe, ukuze abe ngumkandodana yenkosi yakho, njengoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulumile\x + 24.13-15; 24.42-44.\x*.
\v 52 Kwasekusithi inceku kaAbrahama isizwile amazwi abo yakhothamela emhlabathini phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 24.26,48.\x*\nd*.
\v 53 Inceku yasikhupha imiceciso\f + \fk imiceciso: \fl Heb. \fq izitsha.\f* yesiliva, lemiceciso yegolide, lezembatho, yakunika uRebeka, yabanika lomnewabo lonina impahla eziligugu\x + 2 Lan. 21.3; 32.23. Ezra 1.6.\x*.
\v 54 Basebesidla banatha, yona lamadoda ayelayo, balala; bavuka ekuseni, yasisithi: Ngiyekelani ngiye enkosini yami\x + 24.56,59.\x*.
\v 55 Kodwa umnewabo lonina bathi: Kayihlale lathi intombazana izinsuku loba ezilitshumi, emva kwalokho uhambe.
\v 56 Yasisithi kubo: Lingangibambeleli, lokhu iN\nd kosi\nd* iphumelelisile indlela yami; ngiyekelani ngihambe ukuze ngiye enkosini yami.
\v 57 Basebesithi: Asiyibize intombi, sizwe emlonyeni wayo.
\v 58 Basebembiza uRebeka, bathi kuye: Uzahamba lalindoda yini? Wasesithi: Ngizahamba.
\v 59 Basebemyekela ehamba uRebeka udadewabo lomlizane wakhe\x + 35.8.\x*, lenceku kaAbrahama lamadoda ayo.
\v 60 Basebembusisa uRebeka, bathi kuye: Wena dadewethu, woba zinkulungwane zezigidi\x + 17.16.\x*, lenzalo yakho ibe ngumnikazi wesango labayizondayo\x + 22.17.\x*!
\p
\v 61 URebeka wasesukuma lamantombazana akhe, bagada amakamela, balandela indoda; inceku yasimthatha uRebeka, yahamba.
\p
\v 62 UIsaka wasefika lapho abavelela khona emthonjeni iLahayi-Royi\x + 16.14; 25.11.\x*, njalo wayehlala elizweni leningizimu.
\v 63 UIsaka wasephuma ukuyazindla\x + Hlab. 77.6; 119.15,23,48,78,148; 143.5.\x*\f + \fk ukuzindla: \fl kumbe, \fq ukukhuleka.\f* ensimini sekuntambama; waphakamisa amehlo akhe wabona, khangela-ke, amakamela ayesiza.
\v 64 LoRebeka waphakamisa amehlo akhe; esembonile uIsaka waziwisa ekamelweni\x + Josh. 15.18.\x*.
\v 65 Wasesithi encekwini: Ngubani lindoda ehamba emasimini ukusihlangabeza? Inceku yasisithi: Yinkosi yami. Wasethatha isimbombozo, wazigubuzela.
\v 66 Inceku yasilandisa kuIsaka zonke indaba ezenzileyo.
\v 67 UIsaka wasemngenisa ethenteni likaSara unina, wamthatha uRebeka, waba ngumkakhe, wamthanda. UIsaka waseduduzwa\x + 37.35; 38.12. 2 Sam. 13.39.\x* emva \add kokufa\add* kukanina\x + 23.2.\x*.
